# Copilot Context Optimization
# Exclude binary and build artifacts from Copilot context
**/bin/**
**/build/**
**/dist/**
**/vendor/**
**/tmp/**
**/air_tmp/**
**/.next/**
**/.git/**

# Exclude log files
**/*.log
**/*.tmp
**/*.temp

# Exclude large generated files
**/coverage/**
**/.terraform/**
**/.docker/**

# Exclude dependency files to reduce context size
**/go.sum
**/package-lock.json
**/yarn.lock

# Exclude Docker and infrastructure files from context
**/Dockerfile*
**/docker-compose*.yml
**/.dockerignore

# Exclude migration files (usually auto-generated)
**/migrations/**
**/seeds/**

# Exclude documentation that might be large
**/docs/**
**/README.md
**/LICENSE
**/CHANGELOG.md

# Exclude test data
**/testdata/**
**/fixtures/**
**/mocks/**

# Exclude specific large config files
**/.golangci.yml
**/.github/**
**/.gitignore
**/.gitattributes
